name: Have you ever wondered what it's like to be a starving artist ?
description:
Download Hi Res (2.1G) : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QNGbvt5Kp3Ds6Y5h8S2v5_nsS4mkyRXQ/view?usp=sharing 
Download Lo Res (581MB) : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VBDI4dGtTxG9LTvV26Pe-wGrEIzjjYo3/view?usp=sharing 

  Hello fellow Neo-Protopian Creatives. This is my genesis drop ! A 134 minute narrated story telling documentary of my decades living as a starving artist. The challenges, the wins, the fails, the dramas.
  As well as being a guitar player, band leader, recording engineer, music producer and a live sound mixer I also have always been heavily involved in the creating of the art works for the bands I have played in including making music videos – directing, scripting, story boarding, shooting, editing etc.
  The avant-garde and experimental environment created by the early NFT purveyors feels homey to me. My peeps !! I'm so glad I found you. 
  I've got plans. Keep an eye on me !!!
  Enjoy, Kurt
